Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:35.28,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:13.34,Title1E8,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(671,180)}Tea and Distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:13.98,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:15.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You have a stain on your shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:17.63,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:18.72,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,That's Shirakiin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.14,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Is that her boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:20.86,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.15,0:02:23.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:28.83,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I cannot allow you to dirty \Nyour hands with such a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:32.90,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall do anything dirty for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.49,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be your hands and feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.01,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, just hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.52,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.53,0:02:40.97,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:42.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.00,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You look perfect yet again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:48.85,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish to keep gazing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.52,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're never going to \Nlet me leave, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.90,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep humoring you, I'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:56.44,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:02:59.61,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:01.74,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I have inconvenienced you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.96,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I realize
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.96,0:03:08.31,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,that even wishing to be \Nwith you for longer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.23,0:03:12.00,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,is impudence for a mere dog like myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:16.59,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I understand I should feel honored by \Nsimply being allowed to serve you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am a greedy animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.93,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You needn't go that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.93,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying I may wish for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:26.09,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wish away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:29.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask that you exit, \Nthe second your class ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.84,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:33.97,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And then, would you stay \Nwith me after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:35.56,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:40.43,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a kind and wonderful person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.41,Sign08A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(1,646)}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:43.00,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I think I just got played...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:46.08,Default,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:54.73,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:03:59.01,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.46,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is your hand okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.72,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.59,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.64,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You need not worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:10.38,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am your bodyguard precisely \Nfor moments like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:14.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is my honor to be your shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.35,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:27.18,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,why he feels the need to humble \Nhimself to that degree...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.20,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.92,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Did you train today, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:31.84,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:34.12,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I ran all the way to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.70,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.63,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.42,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though the other bodyguard-clients
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:47.18,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,are far more like friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.02,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.98,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me! Me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty gung-ho about participating,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:00.88,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,for such a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.34,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.90,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty kind, for such a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.08,Sign08A,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Cafeteria
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.84,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.53,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:24.22,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You gave me ten yen too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:25.59,Default,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:28.63,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty honest, for such a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:31.26,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.64,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He used to serve him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.64,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not honest at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.12,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he knew who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:41.51,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm that man's fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.57,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He said that I saved him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.84,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it has anything \Nto do with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:56.40,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Shirakiin, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.07,Default,Teach,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.76,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:24.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya's eating a taiyaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.04,0:06:27.11,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:31.81,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He always notices everything about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:33.82,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know anything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.55,0:06:43.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.16,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Meat and potatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.10,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:07:01.88,Sign08B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1460)}Understand \Nhim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:00.59,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,to better understand him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:18.34,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:24.00,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.00,0:07:27.49,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,and even this short distance felt \Nlike a thousand miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.34,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:34.93,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.51,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Where would you like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You said you wanted to be \Nwith me after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:42.39,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that mean you had somewhere \Nyou wanted to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:45.19,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, you cunningly \Nmade me agree to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.78,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:52.48,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,It is impossible for me to expect \Nyou to go anywhere for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.99,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It's that gorgeous car again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.92,0:07:59.58,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.26,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is he devious, or is he really pure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.81,0:08:06.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you actually do \Nwhile you were alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.68,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, today I spent the morning
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:12.29,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,reading the message you sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:13.38,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The entire time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.47,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,How was school, Miss Ririchiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:29.69,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:31.47,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've noticed I spend a lot of time \Nwith Roromiya and Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.79,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Food tastes better when you eat together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:44.46,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.88,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're so rigid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.33,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really in my nature to mingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.81,0:08:53.30,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.72,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:09:00.93,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But Watanuki always has \Na really fancy lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:04.56,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Watanuki's grandpa always brings it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.60,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What a spoiled little rich boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.90,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:13.13,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Roromiya's always trying to feed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.40,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Say "Ahh..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:22.34,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, it isn't fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.47,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to hear that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.39,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:38.88,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he did notice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:43.28,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,that I was worrying about school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:48.37,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And how I'm actually really glad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.09,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,that Roromiya and Watanuki are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:56.78,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I never say what I mean, \Nbut he still notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:01.70,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't know \Nanything about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.26,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to reciprocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.31,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:13.83,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to understand him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:14.82,Sign08B,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,748)\an8}I want to \Nunderstand \Nhim, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:20.97,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Want to eat together, Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:25.86,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like eating with me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:26.89,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.40,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Says the one who already has \Neverything prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:35.28,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to have three paper \Nplates and three paper cups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.20,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a delinquent, so I just happened \Nto be walking past this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.20,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.54,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:49.93,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Eating together makes the food taste better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.46,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,It also makes you closer friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.79,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:57.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,They do say people are defenseless \Nwhile they're feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:10:59.50,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a meal with Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.30,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've never seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.30,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,eat anything since I \Narrived at Ayakashi Kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.60,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:14.52,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Even with that, he takes \Nextra care to humble himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:15.69,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.27,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I must level the field more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.40,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I don't understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:22.57,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Eating together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:24.12,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.67,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.85,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:33.79,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,with all my heart, \Njust like he prepared my tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.31,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my famous coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.71,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,and have tea time with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.14,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.14,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Eating with Chiyo is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:56.54,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:12:00.44,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,The goal is to have tea together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:04.05,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But if we do this, \NI want him to enjoy himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:08.87,Default,Murai,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.62,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't like I expect him to \Nbe grateful or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:13.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,so you can shut up, Murai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:18.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.08,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.38,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Then I just need to invite Miketsukami \Ntomorrow morning, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:32.56,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But how should I invite him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:48.03,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Ways to Invite Miketsukami \NIdea One
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:52.96,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"Miketsukami, I'd like to buy some coffee beans. \NCare to come along?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:57.54,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}"Of course. Will you \Nbe preparing the \Ncoffee yourself?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.88,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"I will, yes. My coffee \Nis quite delectable."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:03.97,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}"I would love to \Ntry some of your \Ntasty beverage."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.59,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,He'd never say anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:11.77,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Idea Two
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:15.31,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"Have you ever heard of Ethiopian \NAndromeda coffee?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.23,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}"What would that be?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:22.86,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"It's an extremely rare variety, \Ngrown entirely wild in the forest. \NI've managed to procure some."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:24.95,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.95,0:13:26.45,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:26.99,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Idea Three
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:31.79,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}"I've discovered a new \Nvariety of coffee. \NHelp me taste it."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:33.98,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I ordering him around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:35.62,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Idea Four
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.88,Sign08C,Text,0000,0000,0000,,"I'd like to drink coffee with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.17,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.18,0:14:08.86,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:14.42,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.04,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:21.21,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But, Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.63,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:25.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I w-was wondering if today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.42,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.68,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.96,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:29.96,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.76,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.97,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you might like to have coffee with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.31,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:42.23,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,T-Today... Co-Co-Co-Co-Co...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.95,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I want some corn potage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.73,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:56.25,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,O-Once we're in the lounge, I'll calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.53,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,How is the corn potage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:08.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.75,0:15:10.34,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am so glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:15.70,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,Say "Ahh."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:18.01,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it, Ririchiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.01,0:15:20.44,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Let Auntie see you getting fed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:21.88,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:24.76,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to turn you into a dust cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.86,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, can you believe her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:28.85,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Say "Ahh," Watanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:30.21,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.28,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how cute. You're embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:32.87,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.15,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:34.97,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.89,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:36.70,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.20,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I need it to be quieter than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.40,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,You're embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.19,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I "ahh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.55,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.34,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:50.01,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I can do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.68,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:55.68,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,First period is Home Ec.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.83,Default,Karuta,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.48,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roromiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.18,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:08.61,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.58,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is the high-level art of inviting others
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:16.03,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,impossible for me, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:19.95,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:24.69,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Ask him when he comes to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.09,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Miss Ririchiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.01,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:35.18,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.71,0:16:43.10,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,W-Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.03,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.30,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you say it's a beautiful day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:51.78,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.50,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Nice boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.81,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:10.05,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that they're losing to \Ngravity is so perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:12.67,Default,Nobara,0000,0000,0000,,You have your eye in the right place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.64,Default,Sorinozuka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:31.54,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Watanuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:34.53,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to rehydrate \Nyourself after your bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.93,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the dog bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:37.93,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to lick that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.45,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:49.19,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.60,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,If you stay with me, \Nsooner or later you'll get hurt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:00.13,Inuboku-flashback,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we try it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.69,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for calling you \Nhere at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:48.62,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:53.38,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am happy to meet you anywhere, \Nat any hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.78,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You've seemed ill at ease all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.43,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something I'm not doing for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:05.05,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.89,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel like I'm being a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:10.13,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:12.31,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:17.07,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You really do observe me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:19.15,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.99,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You were quite pale this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:23.91,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:27.47,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,though you always step into the \Nelevator with your right foot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.47,0:20:29.20,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,this morning, you entered with your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.85,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You also added 1.5 grams more sugar
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.15,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,into your tea than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:39.17,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And though you habitually fasten your \Nseatbelt once you're seated in the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.37,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,today, the car had almost started \Nbefore you fastened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:43.01,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just one second...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:45.27,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,And normally, you wipe your right lens first \Nwhen cleaning your glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:46.52,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,but today, you began with the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:49.36,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,You pour soy sauce clockwise on \Nyour eggs. Yet today, the motion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.07,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,was counter-clockwise, with an \Nextra shake of black pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.44,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, while you were \Nwashing your hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.65,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell have you been looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:59.58,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,At everything that you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:02.82,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No detail is too minor for me to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.99,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I was an idiot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.41,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.72,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And I am certainly not dissatisfied \Nwith you in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:20.25,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But you aren't being fair...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.74,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You only care about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:26.22,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't let me know \Nanything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.51,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.26,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's unpleasant to be in that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I am unworthy of your kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.18,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you'd have \Nsuch compassion for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:37.81,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,when I am but your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.32,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of behavior is exactly \Nwhat I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.10,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:54.56,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,how to interact with someone \Nother than to serve them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.00,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I've spent my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.09,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Miketsukami...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:11.62,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,I am the least qualified person \Nto lecture anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:14.35,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,on how to communicate with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.30,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:21.75,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,the distance between us is far greater
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.19,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,than that of everyone else here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.85,0:22:26.11,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ririchiyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:30.11,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which is why tomorrow, \Nyou're joining me for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.11,0:22:31.53,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll make the coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:34.74,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,During this time, we will be equals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.96,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You are forbidden to be formal with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:46.66,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:48.87,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you hate coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:49.55,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.16,0:22:52.72,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,My head was just so filled with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.86,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,that I lost control of my breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:56.85,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually panting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.94,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,So you can drink coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:10.86,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.32,0:23:16.29,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:17.75,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.18,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:20.29,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.29,0:23:22.57,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:25.80,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yes. If I were to express \Nit in words, I would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.57,0:23:26.70,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, I can only interact with \Nothers in a distorted way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:29.68,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}without it, my world would \Nbe shrouded in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.21,0:23:30.39,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,But today, I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:31.09,Default,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:32.11,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,like I got to know you a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.76,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I could never say enough about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.28,Default,Soushi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}If necessary, I could speak of my love \Nuntil the night turns to dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.28,Inuboku-internal,Ririchiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little like me, \Nand that made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:37.85,Sign08D,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,266)}You're a little like me, \Nand that made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.83,0:23:44.63,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Let the first Ayakashi Kan \Npartner games begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:45.90,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.92,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing games in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:51.01,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, a fateful moment in time \Nwhen the bond between partners is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.19,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:57.04,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Will he understand me? \NDoes he actually understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.04,0:24:00.26,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... Oh, I just can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:02.39,Default,Natsume,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on {\i1}Inu X Boku Secret Service{\i0}:
