Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.40,0:24:04.59,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop ignoring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:05.63,Default,Watanuki,0000,0000,0000,,Zange!
